item.title: CVE-2023-3211|2024-08-02T06:48:08.128Z -- unknown -- wordpress%20database%20administrator
item.description: The WordPress Database Administrator WordPress plugin through 1.0.3 does not properly sanitise and escape a parameter before using it in a SQL statement via an AJAX action available to unauthenticated users, leading to a SQL injection.
